The paper proposes a method for speech enhancement using deep neural networks and optimization techniques. This falls under the domain of speech processing and natural language processing, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.SD and cs.CL. The paper also discusses the use of generative adversarial networks (GANs) and optimization of adversarial loss, which are covered by the sub-categories cs.LG and cs.SI.
